      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 47 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 47 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：臀困于株木，入于幽谷，三歲不見。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows its subject with bare buttocks straitened under the stump of a tree. He enters a dark valley, and for three years has no prospect (of deliverance).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
