      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 47 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 47 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：困于酒食，朱紱方來，利用亨祀，征凶，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject straitened amidst his wine and viands. There come to him anon the red knee-covers (of the ruler). It will be well for him (to maintain his sincerity as) in sacrificing. Active operations (on his part) will lead to evil, but he will be free from blame.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
