      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 47 六三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 47 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：困于石，據于蒺藜，入于其宮，不見其妻，凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows its subject straitened before a (frowning) rock. He lays hold of thorns. He enters his palace, and does not see his wife. There will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
