      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 47 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 47 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：來徐徐，困于金車，吝，有終。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided shows its subject proceeding very slowly (to help the subject of the first line), who is straitened by the carriage adorned with metal in front of him. There will be occasion for regret, but the end will be good.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
