      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 47 九五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 47 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：劓刖，困于赤紱，乃徐有說，利用祭祀。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows its subject with his nose and feet cut off. He is straitened by (his ministers in their) scarlet aprons. He is leisurely in his movements, however, and is satisfied. It will be well for him to be (as sincere) as in sacrificing (to spiritual beings).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
